{"id":158400,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/联合早报-天旱已久湖南迎来大雨/","date":"2011-06-06T13:00:24Z","modified":"2011-06-06T13:00:24Z","title":"联合早报 | 天旱已久湖南迎来大雨","content":"<div>\n<p>天旱已久湖南迎来大雨</p>\n<p>（2011-06-06）</p>\n<table align=\"left\" width=\"306\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td>\n早报导读</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/wapzb.shtml\"><img width=\"300\" height=\"250\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://www.zaobao.com/ssi/bizp/svc/wap300_110421.gif\" /></a></p>\n<table width=\"300\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/special/hotspot/shangrilaD.shtml\">[香格里拉对话]</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/special/hotspot/pages/hotspot110606.shtml\">通过多方对话维护区域安全</a><br /><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/special/hotspot/taiwan_food.shtml\">[塑化剂风波]</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/special/hotspot/pages/hotspot110606a.shtml\">塑化剂风波 殃及台湾烘焙业</a><br /><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/special/china/taiwan/taiwan.shtml\">[台海局势]</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/special/china/taiwan/pages13/taiwan110606.shtml\">台湾人才挺进大陆势不可挡</a><br /><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/special/china/zaodian/zaodian.shtml\">[中国早点]</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/special/china/zaodian/pages2/zaodian_jing110606.shtml\">李娜争得感谢的自由与权利</a></p>\n<table width=\"300\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/special/services/pages/recruitment_110208a.html\"><strong>联合早报网招聘 Freelance网络新闻编辑</strong></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p>简讯</p>\n<p> （北京讯）天旱已久的湖南连日迎来大雨，但大雨成灾，湘西自治州、怀化、娄底等地出现洪涝灾情，灾民多达61万7400人。</p>\n<p> 前日凌晨1时，湘西凤凰县13个自动雨量站出现大暴雨，持续10余小时的暴雨使得中国最美古城之一的湘西凤凰一度陷入水困。</p>\n<p> 凤凰沱江水当日上涨超过3米，沱江沿河两岸及古城低洼处部分民房和商铺进水，水深达1.3米左右。凤凰至吉首209国道，因洪水漫过公路及塌方，一度造成交通中断。</p>\n<p> 中午过后，降水减弱，凤凰沱江洪水水位逐步回落，当地中断的交通恢复正常。贵州、湖北等五省也都出现较大范围的强降雨天气。</p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.zaobao.com%2Fzg%2Fzg110606_006.shtml&#038;title=%E5%A4%A9%E6%97%B1%E5%B7%B2%E4%B9%85%E6%B9%96%E5%8D%97%E8%BF%8E%E6%9D%A5%E5%A4%A7%E9%9B%A8\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}